Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.46,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}You just call up circuit zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.96,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}"思い"それが渦巻いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.73,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ここは僕らの戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.54,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}少し先の理想すら追えない{\fsp1}…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.95,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉 一つのみ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.28,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 そっと閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.18,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}今はただ 振動に応えた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.23,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}心の瞳(め)で Lock-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.98,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}君が叫ぶ Push up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.69,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}この痛みと熱さが答だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.00,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-キミハマダ戦エル-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.60,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}幻聴か?否か?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:30.32,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}<回路=意識>(カイロ)を意思で導け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:35.58,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}決してのみ込まれるな 無限の谷へと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:41.34,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}目の前の不条理を壊せ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.92,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Can you break up endless war?
Comment: 1,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.46,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}You just call up circuit zone!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.96,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}"思绪"扰乱心中平静
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.73,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这里是我们的战场
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.54,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}连眼前的理想都无法追寻{\fsp1}…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.95,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言语 咽回腹中
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.28,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}记忆 锁在心里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.18,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}如今只要 回应这振动就好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.23,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}睁开心眼 Lock-on!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.98,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}你在呼喊 Push up!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.69,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这痛楚和灼热便是答案!!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.00,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-你还能继续战斗-
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这是幻听吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.60,0:03:30.32,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}意识 用意志来引导
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.42,0:03:35.58,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}谨记不要被吞入 那不见底的深渊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.58,0:03:41.34,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}击溃眼前的荒唐不经!
Comment: 1,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.92,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Can you break up endless war?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:14.25,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見つめ合う  心  ひらいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:20.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}強がりと弱さのループ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:26.90,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ねえ少しは  慣れたはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:36.97,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉にしても全てのことは  わからないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:41.48,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}それだけは覚えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:44.69,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}こんなものじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:48.03,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}自分に気付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:55.23,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}勇気に乗せたなら  世界は変わっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:23:03.00,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}独りじゃ知らなかった  あのTELEPATHY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:09.47,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}導く  後ろ姿  とても眩しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:16.50,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}だから私は  目をそらさず君を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:23.42,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}届くと  信じている
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.09,0:22:14.25,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}对视凝望  将心扉敞开
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.65,0:22:20.20,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}逞强与软弱的循环
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.54,0:22:26.90,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}呐  是不是  略微习惯了些
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.32,0:22:36.97,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}即便用语言阐述  也不是一切事情  都能清晰明了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.43,0:22:41.48,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我只记住了这个道理
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.62,0:22:44.69,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}并不是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.03,0:22:48.03,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}自己去发现
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.40,0:22:55.23,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}只要拿出勇气前行  世界会随之改变
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.83,0:23:03.00,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}独自一人绝不可能注意到  那TELEPATHY
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.66,0:23:09.47,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}引领我的那个背影  如此光辉耀眼
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.69,0:23:16.50,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}所以我目不转睛  一直注视着你
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.12,0:23:23.42,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}相信你会懂我的心
